item.title: CVE-2018-1808|2024-08-05T04:14:38.558Z -- ibm -- websphere%20commerce
item.description: IBM WebSphere Commerce 9.0.0.0 through 9.0.0.6 could allow some server-side code injection due to inadequate input control. IBM X-Force ID: 149828.

item.title: CVE-2018-1644|2024-08-05T04:07:44.099Z -- ibm -- websphere%20commerce
item.description: IBM WebSphere Commerce Enterprise, Professional, Express, and Developer 9.0.0.0 - 9.0.0.4, 8.0.0.0 - 8.0.0.19, 8.0.1.0 - 8.0.1.13, 8.0.3.0 - 8.0.3.6, 8.0.4.0 - 8.0.4.14, and 7.0.0.0 Feature Pack 8 could allow an authenticated user to obtain sensitive information about another user.
